<item>
            <title>[SPARK-48184] Always set the seed of dataframe.sample in Client side</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-48184</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the output dataframe of `sample` is not immutable in Spark Connect&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In Spark Classic:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
In [1]: df = spark.range(10000).sample(0.1)
In [2]: [df.count() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i in range(10)]
Out[2]: [1006, 1006, 1006, 1006, 1006, 1006, 1006, 1006, 1006, 1006]&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In Spark Connect:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
In [1]: df = spark.range(10000).sample(0.1)
In [2]: [df.count() &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; i in range(10)]
Out[2]: [969, 1005, 958, 996, 987, 1026, 991, 1020, 1012, 979]
 &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
